        </div>
        <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
            <svg class="svg-icon">
                <use xlink:href="#support-included"></use>
            </svg>
            <h3>Support included</h3>
            <p class="p-icon">Each plan includes a free support time
                and access to the developers forum.
                Also, large community is supporting us.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

